Det er ikke en af mine favoritter.

961
01:20:56.434 --> 01:20:59.935
Det bliver okay.

962
01:21:00.859 --> 01:21:03.985
Okay?

963
01:21:04.153 --> 01:21:07.029
Okay.

964
